title: Effects of taxes and benefits on household income [Financial Year Ending 2019]
publisher: International trade in services by subnational areas of the UK: 2018
description: Average annual incomes, taxes and benefits, and household characteristics of retired and non-retired households in the UK. Data for financial years, by quintile and decile groups, country and region and tenure type.
datasetNotes: On landing page scroll down to latest dataset under heading "Your download option".
